{"tid":1590006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉屯門燒國旗　13 歲女童遭落案起訴　周五提堂","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:53:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2811cc04495296da47d167e361d119cc1552129","tid":1590006,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chinaflag-12_qzda5_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchinaflag-12_qzda5_1200x0.png&h=91e44045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方前日（21日）拘捕一名 13 歲女童涉嫌「侮辱國旗」，女童被扣留近 20 小時後獲准保釋候查。警方今日正式落案起訴女童一項「侮辱國旗」罪，案件將於星期五（27日）在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n周六（21日）有人發起「屯門公園再光復」行動，遊行隊頭於下午 3 點 40 分到達屯門政府合署後，十多名示威者將屯門大會堂外的中國國旗拆下踐踏，並以大量紙巾助燃將國旗焚燒，消防員十分鐘後到場將火救熄。警方經調查後，於同日傍晚約 6 時 30 分在荃灣拘捕一名 13 歲本地女童，帶返警署通宵扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n同案男子今提堂  獲保釋須遵宵禁令<br />\n<br />\n另外，就同一宗案件，另一名 21 歲姓鄧男子亦於昨日（22日）被警方以涉嫌「侮辱國旗」罪拘捕及起訴，案件已於今日在屯門裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n被告暫時毋須答辯，裁判官批准備被告以 5000 元保釋，但須遵守宵禁令及一星期到警署報到兩次。案件將押後到 11 月 27 日再提堂，以待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n而就昨日（22日）有示威者在沙田新城市廣場內踐踏及將國旗投入城門河，警方昨晚拘捕一名21歲姓羅本地男子。被捕男子目前仍被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E7%87%92%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-13-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%81%AD%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obp6X7PLg0GRX82CuX%2BG2FI0%3D&h=a4e2a115\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597-13-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%2F&h=dcfe5f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B6%89%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E7%87%92%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97-13-%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E7%AB%A5%E9%81%AD%E8%90%BD%E6%A1%88%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4-%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82/</a>"},{"pid":"c5a9b4c022af376876e6f9c29ee45697b87ac9bd","tid":1590006,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"2324b54582a9c8a7ee0a9d772525aaa29da78acd","tid":1590006,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}